	<h1 class="title">Apple Pay 扩大使用范围，要做网页支付和积分系统</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/97532/small/97532.jpeg?1431064746" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赵长存 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-07 07:57:23 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/26455/medium/26455.jpg?1462427471" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


